spec_data.Name: python2-stomper
spec_data.Description:
This is a python client implementation of the STOMP protocol. The client is
attempting to be transport layer neutral. This module provides functions to
create and parse STOMP messages in a programatic fashion.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sat 29 Jul 2017 04:28:33 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A python client implementation of the STOMP protocol
